text: Good morning <@U1F3CQ2HX> and @ashish. Yes, noted. There are several threads/discussion about APIs these days. I get the feeling that going forward we are more likely to extend the gRPC API rather than enhance (or fix) some of the REST API calls we have. For starters, the gRPC is indeed richer already....

For the "interested reader/follower/contributor": a larger change that is proposed can be tracked here  <https://jira.hyperledger.org/browse/FAB-16> (trying to avoid using the username-pass pairs altogether...)
